name: Haste-server
body:
# Pastebin

haste-server is an open source pastebin.  You can see an example at [hastebin.com](http://hastebin.com), and it's easy to install locally.

## GitHub

Check out the project on [github](https://github.com/seejohnrun/haste-server)
tagline: open source pastebin written in node.js
